# Product Context

- Gugugram is a pixel-art social network; preserve this domain intent in features.
- User-facing language is Brazilian Portuguese (`pt-BR`) unless explicitly requested otherwise.
- Image posting features must respect square pixel-art constraints and allowed tiny dimensions.
- Prioritize consistency with existing social features (profiles, friends, comments, messages).

## Tech Snapshot

- Astro SSR + Svelte components, PostgreSQL (Neon), Drizzle ORM, better-auth.
- Keep implementations aligned with current stack and existing project patterns.
